========================================================================
probe_capability_token.py — Echo→Sys8 Direct Application Patterns
========================================================================

=== CATEGORY A: echo(g(N))(sys8)(QD/nil) — direct application ===
  echo(g(N)) returns Left(g(N)) = λl.λr.l(g(N))
  Applied to sys8: Left(g(N))(sys8)(QD) → sys8(g(N))(QD)
  But lazy evaluation might change behavior!

  [A1:echo(g251)(sys8)(QD)] (23B, bc=0efbfd08fd0500fd000500fd03fdfefd02fdfefdfefdff)... Right(6) = PermDenied
  [A2:echo(g252)(sys8)(QD)] (23B, bc=0efcfd08fd0500fd000500fd03fdfefd02fdfefdfefdff)... Right(6) = PermDenied
